bearded dragon my husband wants to get a bearded dragon as a pet i'm not so sure i've never been a huge fan of reptiles we have heard great things about their personalites though we met someone that said theirs even got along with their cats and would sit at the window with them i just can't picture a reptile being so friendly i would love to hear people's experiences with these little guys thanks well i have bearded dragons at first i wanted a pet reptile an i didnt no wat get but wen i heard bout these i wanted kuz they sounded reley cool an freindly good children not to young tho an wen i got it mi mum wasnt to happy with a lizred because mi mum h z snakes an all that sorta stuff like reptiles but after a few weekz she gt atached them at first she didnt hold them an kept well away but now she iz kissing them an feeding them now reley gd fun to have they like the window cill an they lke there greens they like strawberrys azwell but the worse fing iz the criccets u feed them an if u do get make shaw itz perked up an healthy or waste ov money an may die great to have my i chose wen they were little an now quite old an i didnt no wat sex they were an they turned out to be both males witch then they started fighting after a wile boy or girl or girl an girl if u choose get they also hav there funny moments as well they bob there heds for dominnance an then puff there cheek out an turn black the boys ones also the females seem to wave there arm at ppl dnt no y but waving the females do this mainly plus giv it a bath az well u kan if u want itz juz like havin a baby welll if u do get your life will be more fun it has made myn but u have too fink about the holidays an that u karnt leve them on there own at least day max they need attentoin daily not so mutch with tho well all the best on your beardy Little Britain Shaggy dog story About a Boy Bearded Dragon Friends EastEnders SpongeBob SquarePants Care Bears Academy Award for Original Music Score Phoebe Buffay's songs Gre